      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ADHANA MADI (6) has a strong record this trip with two wins and two placings from six starts. Scored by 9 lengths last time (39.26) in a Grade 5/6 over 680m at Murray Bridge. Looks well placed and should feature. URANA SPACE (4) goes very well this trip starting five times for two wins and two minors. Was out of placings last time (43.08) at this track in a OPEN, finishing fourth and beaten 4.5 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. QUICK STRIKE (2) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish third, beaten 1.5 lengths (35.33) at this track in a Grade 5/6 over 595m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Can feature again. PAW LOUIS (1) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.",
